This is an application using SimpleHTTPServer to
serve a different index page. The index page is generated within
code. It shows images within specified directory on the page. It
shows 20 images at first, showing 20 more on clicking the 'more'
link until all images are shown. The order of images is randomized.

I think this can be used for a porn website.

Usage: pygallerypage.py [options] [DIR [PORT]]

Options:
  --version             show program's version number and exit
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -d DIR, --directory=DIR
                        Run in directory DIR
  -p PORT, --port=PORT  Run on port PORT


